Fetal HR avg value.normal_values: For Fetal HR 120 to 160 bpm is normal range
Fetal HR avg value.abnormal_values: For Fetal HR <120 bpm and >160 bpm is abnormal range

AFI cm value.normal_values: For AFI 5 to 25 cm value is considered as normal
AFI cm value.abnormal_values: For AFI  <5 cm and >25 cm value is considered as abnormal

AFI pctl value.normal_values: For AFI 5th to 95th percentile is considered as normal
AFI pctl value.abnormal_values: For AFI <5th percentile and >95th percentile is considered as abnormal

Gender.normal_values: Male and Female is normal values of gender

Fetal Position.normal_values: Normal Fetal positions are Head down (vertex), Anterior and Posterior
Fetal Position.abnormal_values: Abnormal Fetal positions are  Transverse and Head up (breech)

Placenta Location.normal_values: Normal placenta location are Anterior, Posterior, Fundal
Placenta Location.abnormal_values: Abnormal placenta location are Placenta Previa,vasa previa,Accreta,Percreta,Marginal and Low-lying,

Placenta Grade.normal_values: Placenta Grade <=2 is considered as normal
Placenta Grade.abnormal_values: Placenta Grade 3 or more considered as abnormal

Amniotic Fluid.normal_values: Value of Amniotic Fluid Adequate or Normal is fine.
Amniotic Fluid.abnormal_values: Abnormal values fo Amniotic Fluid are Low, High, Oligohydramnios and Polyhydramnios

Fetal Movements.normal_values: Normal values of Fetal Movements are Regular, frequent Or 2
Fetal Movements.abnormal_values: Abnormal values of Fetal Movements are Decreased, Absent, Hyperactive Or <=1

Fetal Tone.normal_values: Normal Values of Fetal Tones is Normal Or 2
Fetal Tone.abnormal_values: Abnormal values of Fetal Tones are Hypotonia Hypertonia Or <=1

Fetal Breathing Move.normal_values: Normal Values of Fetal Breathing Move are Present Or 2
Fetal Breathing Move.abnormal_values: Abnormal Values of Fetal Breathing Move are Absent Or <=1

Amniotic Fluid Volume.normal_values: Normal values of Amniotic Fluid volume are Normal,Adequate Or 2
Amniotic Fluid Volume.abnormal_values: Abnormal values of Amniotic Fluid volume are Low, High, Oligohydramnios, Polyhydramnios Or <=1

Total out of 8.normal_values: Normal Value of Total out of 8 is 8
Total out of 8.abnormal_values: Abnormal value of Total out of 8 is <8
